snippet.textDisplay: Greetings from Macau China! 🇲🇴 We rub some tiger balm 🐯 on the palms palm👐🏻, inhale (breath in from the nose) 👃🏻several times. This is to protect the respiratory system 🫁 against virus 🦠 . Whenever heading out and coming home, I will do it. God bless Indonesia!! 🇮🇩 Stay Strong! 💪🏻💪🏻
